<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>BECRU Inmobiliaria - Inicio</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/becru_logo.jpg">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/landing.css">
</head>
<body>

  <div class="top-bar">
    <div class="left-info">
      <span class="phone">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-phone">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
        </svg>
        232 159 6250
      </span>
      <span class="email">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-mail">
          <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/>
          <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
        </svg>
        becru_sa@outlook.com
      </span>
      <span class="address">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-map-pin">
          <path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
        </svg>
        Jorege Todd No. 101 Col. Santana Maloapan Martínez de La Torre
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="right-info">
      <div class="social-icons">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/becruasesor" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Facebook">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-facebook">
            <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/" class="logo">
      <img src="/images/becru_logo.jpg" alt="BECRU Inmobiliaria Logo">
      Becru Inmobiliaria
    </a>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#about">Sobre Nosotros</a></li>
      <li><a href="#services">Servicios</a></li>
      <li><a href="#propiedades">Propiedades</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contacto</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="section-container carousel-section">
    <div class="carousel-container">
      <div class="carousel-track" id="carouselTrack">
        <% if (properties && properties.length) { %>
          <% properties.forEach((property) => { %>
            <div class="carousel-slide">
              <img src="<%= property.coverImage ? property.coverImage.filepath : '/images/property-placeholder.jpg' %>"
                alt="Propiedad <%= property.title %>" class="carousel-image">
              <div class="property-details">
                <h3><%= property.title %></h3>
                <p><%= property.ubication || 'Ubicación no disponible' %></p>
                <div class="property-icons">
                  <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-bed">
                      <path d="M3 20v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8"/>
                      <path d="M5 10V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4"/>
                      <path d="M3 18h18"/>
                    </svg> <%= property.number_of_rooms || 0 %>
                  </span>
                  <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-shower">
                      <path d="M4 4l2.5 2.5"/>
                      <path d="M13.5 6.5a4.95 4.95 0 0 0-7 7"/>
                      <path d="M15 5L5 15"/>
                      <path d="M14 17v.01"/>
                      <path d="M10 16v.01"/>
                      <path d="M13 13v.01"/>
                      <path d="M16 10v.01"/>
                      <path d="M11 20v.01"/>
                      <path d="M17 14v.01"/>
                      <path d="M20 11v.01"/>
                    </svg> <%= property.number_of_bathrooms || 0 %>
                  </span>
                  <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-ruler">
                      <line x1="2" y1="22" x2="22" y2="2"></line>
                      <line x1="2" y1="2" x2="22" y2="22"></line>
                    </svg> <%= property.area || '0 m²' %>
                  </span>
                  <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-house">
                      <path d="M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8"/>
                      <path d="M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-5.999a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 5.999A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
                    </svg> <%= property.land_area || '0 m²' %>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="property-price">
                  $<%= property.price.toLocaleString() %>
                </div>
                <a href="/propiedades/<%= property.id %>" class="btn-view-more">Ver Más</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="carousel-slide">
            <h3>No hay propiedades disponibles</h3>
            <p>Vuelve pronto para ver nuevas ofertas.</p>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-btn prev-btn" id="prevBtn">&#10094;</button>
      <button class="carousel-btn next-btn" id="nextBtn">&#10095;</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container about" id="about">
    <h1>Sobre BECRU Inmobiliaria</h1>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Fundada hace cuatro años, BECRU Inmobiliaria se ha consolidado como una empresa comprometida con la calidad, la transparencia y la innovación en el mercado inmobiliario. Nuestro equipo se dedica a brindar soluciones integrales para la compra, venta y gestión de propiedades, ofreciendo un servicio personalizado y profesional.</p>
    </div>
  </div>



  <div class="section-container contact" id="contact">
    <h2>Contáctanos</h2>
    <form action="/contact" method="POST">
      <label for="name">Nombre</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
      <label for="email">Correo Electrónico</label>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
      <label for="message">Mensaje</label>
      <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Enviar Mensaje</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-logo">
          <img src="/images/becru_logo.jpg" alt="BECRU Inmobiliaria Logo">
          <span>BECRU Inmobiliaria</span>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="#about">Sobre Nosotros</a>
          <a href="#propiedades">Propiedades</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contacto</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>© 2025 BECRU Inmobiliaria. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
        <p>Jorege Todd No. 101 Col. Santana Maloapan Martínez de La Torre</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/landing.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
